channel.title: How to get started?
channel.description:
Hey I'm just getting into MoparScape and was wondering how do I get it started? The load window only gives me a "Username", "Password", and "Server IP" button, but some of my friends were saying you need to need other things to load a server. It keeps giving me an error when I just type in a persons server number... Can anyone please help me?
Thanks.[br][size=1]Posted on: April 27, 2007, 10:27:34 PM[/size][hr]Anyone, please?
